Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管那些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑嗎 的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面也必須盡快設下結界 否則就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化貓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半刻前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是小姐的出閣之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥是賣不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是賣藥郎來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是賣藥郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說加世 看看你磨蹭多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 馬上就做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你當今天是什麼日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來送東西的嗎 有什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是來賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可沒那個閒工夫 因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是真央小姐出嫁到志和野家的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這跟我們這些傭人無關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概再過半刻左右來迎接的就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜岡 把障子拉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是夫人這樣就不能通風了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 也就一會工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出嫁嗎 那可太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裏有最適合新嫁娘用的藥...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 不過...讓我看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人 快滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏可不是你這種人能進來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 加世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水的話就快進來喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 回去晚了小心騰山大人發火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用說的那麼過分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點出去 否則饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也忒嚴厲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 看到他就讓人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 比起這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 知道 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這邊是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這藥賣給真央小姐還真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對方的新郎呀 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那新娘子也太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是因為對方承擔了這個家的債務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到出發時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好侍奉公婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬要保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人伊顥大人雖然是個好人 就是不擅長理財
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水江夫人面前好像也抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊國大人嘛也是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則你想怎麼輪到弟弟伊行大人繼承家道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 竟然給你說了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏子管家知道了怕又要發火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為回報 我讓你看一樣好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是老鼠罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 這裏好像有很多捕鼠器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買隻貓不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呀 聽說是因為有人討厭貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過彌平才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你竟然在這裏閒聊消磨時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在說捕老鼠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世 去取水來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到龜都太渴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主 真央小姐 特來迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 要照顧自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 阪井家的盛衰就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候裏子去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央 起身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問一句 討厭貓的原因是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠是子孫繁榮的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真央有福氣喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊 有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你是怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是殺手所為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 對方也不是刀所能殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人 從哪裏進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是加 加世擅自...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行跡可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑嗎 的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面也必須盡快設下結界 否則就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 已經沒氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看與其找醫生不如直接找和尚了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊 國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是你 都是因為你)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(夫人 你冷靜下來)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(伊國 伊國 伊國 都怪你 都是你...)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道嗎 嘿 這樣最好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都是你 都是因為你...)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動 要是像剛才那樣逃跑的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我在裏面貼上符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話還來的及用結界封起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 住口 我看你是打算藉機逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把他綁緊一點如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙會使用很怪異的武術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂已經斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣最好 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有檢查他的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真央小姐會不會是被下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 剛才才說是被砍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣 但不是毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個盒子裏是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這刀是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼賣藥的人要帶著刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了殺死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒教養的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水江大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼妖怪 真不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼暗器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼暗器 裏面沒有設機關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能拔開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是不到時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這刀只有在被殺妖怪的形.實.式合一時才能拔開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾吧 我是一個很無趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可饒恕 送他到番所去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情鬧大的話 我們會比較被動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騰山大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是現在家裏最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水江夫人 水江夫人 水江夫人 水江夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫醫生來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去請坪內先生來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌平最好還是別出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界不是很完整
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 千萬不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說是水江夫人身體不適所以來請先生去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志和野家那邊也派人去傳個話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主 那個還不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了真央猝死 志和野家會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志和野知道還好說 要是主君知道了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好辦法就是說真央得了急病 爭取一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧 騰山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的話反而會適得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們的嘴是無論如何也堵不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情已經惡化到不得不隱瞞的時候了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不如此 你不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為當務之急不是去志和野家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是開誠公佈地請求幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們早這麼做的話 管他志和野家如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的企圖 你就坦白說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是替家主擔心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果騰山大人你說我有企圖的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就請你說說看我有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手段我領教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要點燈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世 真央小姐那裏的燈也點上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 屍體...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何 你不會是不想去吧 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來點燈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田島大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 這些都是妖怪所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼胡話啊 怎麼可能有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 很快就會抓住兇手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田島大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你聽到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼呀 小田島 你別嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌平還沒回來嗎 怎麼要用這麼長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也有他們的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊可是大事 就是有安排也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓多話的可是騰山你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 也太遲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田島 你看見什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棟房子裏面是沒有貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從傭人們發出的尖叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌平 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裏來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些礙事的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個人在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家和真央小姐在奉安車裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人待著很危險 最好和大伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 裝神弄鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 那傢伙進不來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你搞什麼鬼 看我來揭穿你的鬼把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情形暫時穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西啊 完全看不清蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦離開結界就會成為它的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界也不能保持太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去早晚會支撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來必須殺死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 拔開除魔劍需要條件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須把妖怪的形.真實.理指示給除魔劍才能拔開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先就是妖怪的形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是只化貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪成形需要人類的因果和緣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 關於這眾生.真實和理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續

